title: Man Detained In Relation To Case Of Missing 84-Year-Old Nancy Guthrie | 10 News
description: A man has been detained and is being questioned over the baffling disappearance of Nancy Guthrie, the mother of U.S. TV star Savannah Guthrie.  The development follows the release of new security camera footage showing a masked and armed man at the front door of her Tucson home on the night she vanished. title: Protester With Broken Back Speaks Out, Cheating Scandal Rocks Olympics | 10 News+
description: A grandmother who claims she was assaulted by police during a violent protest in Sydney, is calling for the officers involved to face charges and she’s not the only one.  It's one of the worst unsolved cases in Australia. A little girl who disappeared on a NSW beach 56 years ago.  The family of Cheryl Grimmer have delivered a heartbreaking appeal to the NSW Attorney-General and Premier for fresh charges to be laid against the man who confessed to killing her, but is still walking the streets.
